sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant TG as Telegram Bot
    participant Agent as Zico Agent<br/>(lending_agent)
    participant Backend as Lending Service<br/>(:3006)
    participant Miniapp as MiniApp Frontend
    participant Wallet as Thirdweb Wallet
    participant VL as ValidatedLending.sol
    participant Benqi as Benqi Protocol<br/>(Avalanche)

    User->>TG: "Supply 100 USDC on Benqi"
    TG->>Agent: Forward message
    Agent->>Agent: Semantic routing -> LENDING intent
    Agent->>Agent: Collect lending parameters (action=supply, token=USDC, amount=100)
    Agent-->>TG: lending_intent_ready + metadata
    TG-->>User: "Supply 100 USDC on Benqi (APY: 4.2%)" + [Review] button

    User->>Miniapp: Opens lending page
    Miniapp->>Backend: GET /lending/markets
    Backend-->>Miniapp: Markets data (rates, liquidity, health factors)

    User->>Miniapp: Confirms supply

    Note over Miniapp,VL: Two-step flow: approve + supply

    Miniapp->>Wallet: 1. Approve USDC spending
    Wallet->>Miniapp: approval tx receipt

    Miniapp->>Backend: POST /lending/prepare-supply {token: USDC, amount: 100}
    Backend-->>Miniapp: PreparedTx {to: ValidatedLending, data: validateAndSupplyERC20(...)}

    Miniapp->>Wallet: 2. Sign supply transaction
    Wallet->>VL: validateAndSupplyERC20(qUSDC, 100)
    VL->>VL: Pay validation tax
    VL->>Benqi: qToken.mint(100 USDC)
    Benqi-->>User: qUSDC minted (interest-bearing)

    Miniapp->>Miniapp: Track via Gateway API
    Miniapp-->>User: "Supplied 100 USDC. Earning 4.2% APY"
